# INTERIOR::DISABLE_METRO_SYSTEM

## Summary
To turn off all metro system & remove all cost associated with it

## Parameters
* **BOOL** disable

## Notes
<!-- AUTOGENERATED: Remove this line before editing -->
completely disable the metro system in the game
